        <div2>
          <head>
            <title type="main">
              <hi rend="b">LOS’S VISIT</hi>
            </title>
          </head>
		<q>
Your increasing energy<lb/>
amazes me. While I slept,<lb/>
you worked through the night,<lb/>
single-handedly, in bright,<lb/>
black letters, writing,<lb/>
and making dawn come again.<lb/>
<lb/>
I wept when you left,<lb/>
but the vision of your delight makes you beautiful,<lb/>
beyond my words or yours.<lb/>
As you leave, with the new day,<lb/>
in your arms, you carry the sun.
</q>
